snippet.title: Flipper Slipper/フリッパースリッパー (MSX, 1983, ASCII/Spectravideo)
snippet.description: This is Flipper Slipper/フリッパースリッパー for MSX and it's a pinball game will two curve paddles and you can brick the blocks that are protecting the Dog and if the ball is missed four times than water will fill up and it spells Game Over and it has different modes that will make the difficulty increase fast and it's a really good game despite it only getting one version and nothing else which is just sad.
